ygData.messageBody:
oh my that is too funny, a friend of mine called me up and said come
to the arena and help us take down this necro, im like ok. I get
ther and we finish off a 50 pally and my friend says go take down
briyn (lol he goes anon so i had no idea what lvl he was) so i walk
into the arena and attack and 5 seconds later i was dead. He
snared , rooted dotted whatever. It is funny how small the world is
that's for sure. My friend was like oh my god i was joking hes a 65.
But i learned a few valuable lessons that day. while i would love to
spy on him i am now fearful of his capabilities lol.
